msgid ""
"The power contour plot shows how the sensitivity of the test changes with "
"the hypothetical effect size and the sample sizes in the design. As we "
"increase the sample sizes, smaller effect sizes become reliably detectable."
msgstr ""
"檢定力等值線圖顯示檢定的敏感度如何隨假設效果量及設計中的樣本數而變化。當樣本"
"數增加時，較小的效果量也能被可靠地偵測到。"

msgid ""
"Conversely, if one is satisfied to reliably detect only larger effect sizes, "
"smaller sample sizes are needed. The point shows the power of the specified "
"design and effect size."
msgstr ""
"反之，若僅滿足於可靠地偵測較大的效果量，則所需的樣本數較小。圖中的點即表示指"
"定設計與效果量下的檢定力。"

