msgid "have power of at least %1$s"
msgstr "具有至少 %1$s 的檢定力"

msgid "only be sufficiently sensitive (power >%1$s)"
msgstr "僅在檢定力 >%1$s 時才具備足夠的敏感度"

msgid ""
"The power curve above shows how the sensitivity of the test and design is "
"larger for larger effect sizes. If we obtained %1$s our test and design "
"would %2$s to effect sizes of %3$s%4$s."
msgstr ""
"上方的檢定力曲線顯示，對於較大的效果量，檢定與設計的敏感度也較高。若我們獲得 "
"%1$s，則我們的檢定與設計對於 %3$s%4$s 的效果量將 %2$s。"

msgid ""
"We would be more than likely to miss (power less than 50%%) effect sizes "
"less than %1$s%2$s."
msgstr ""
"對於小於 %1$s%2$s 的效果量，我們將很有可能無法偵測到（檢定力低於 50%%）。"

msgid "sample sizes of at least %1$s"
msgstr "至少 %1$s 的樣本數"

msgid ""
"The power curve above shows how the sensitivity of the test and design is "
"larger for larger effect sizes. In order for our test and design to have "
"sufficient sensitivity (power > %1$s) to detect that %2$s when the effect "
"size is %3$s or larger, we would need %4$s."
msgstr ""
"上方的檢定力曲線顯示，對於較大的效果量，檢定與設計的敏感度也較高。為了使我們"
"的檢定與設計在效果量為 %3$s 或以上時，具有足夠的敏感度（檢定力 > %1$s）以偵測"
"到該 %2$s，我們將需要 %4$s。"

msgid "a sample size of %1$s"
msgstr "樣本數為 %1$s"

msgid ""
"The figure above shows two sampling distributions: the sampling distribution "
"of the %1$s effect size when %2$s (left), and when %3$s%4$s (right)."
msgstr ""
"上圖顯示兩個抽樣分配：左側為當 %2$s 時 %1$s 效果量的抽樣分配，右側為當 "
"%3$s%4$s 時的抽樣分配。"

msgid "Both assume %1$s."
msgstr "兩者皆假設 %1$s。"

msgid ""
"The vertical dashed lines show the %1$s we would set for a %2$s test with "
"%3$s."
msgstr "垂直虛線表示我們針對具有 %3$s 的 %2$s 檢定所設定的 %1$s。"

msgid ""
"When the observed effect size is far enough away from 0 to be more extreme "
"than the %1$s we say we 'reject' the null hypothesis."
msgstr ""
"當觀察到的效果量與0的距離足夠遠，以致比 %1$s 更為極端時，我們稱之為「拒絕」虛"
"無假設。"

msgid ""
"If the null hypothesis were true and %1$s the evidence would lead us to "
"wrongly reject the null hypothesis at most %2$s%% of the time."
msgstr ""
"若虛無假設為真且 %1$s，則證據會導致我們錯誤拒絕虛無假設的機率最多為 %2$s%%。"

msgid ""
"On the other hand, if %1$s%2$s, the evidence would exceed the criterion  "
"&mdash; and hence we would correctly claim that %3$s &mdash; at least %4$s%% "
"of the time."
msgstr ""
"另一方面，若 %1$s%2$s，則證據會超過判斷準則 — 因此我們至少有 %4$s%% 的機率會"
"正確地宣稱 %3$s。"

msgid "The design's power for detecting effects of %1$s%2$s is thus %3$s."
msgstr "因此，該設計對於偵測 %1$s%2$s 效果量的檢定力為 %3$s。"

msgid ""
"Due to the rounding of the sample size, the actual power can deviate from "
"the target power."
msgstr "由於樣本數進位的緣故，實際的檢定力可能會偏離目標檢定力。"

msgid "Actual power:"
msgstr "實際檢定力："

msgid "a sample size of %s"
msgstr "樣本數為 %s"

msgid ""
"We would need %1$s to reliably (with probability greater than or equal to "
"%2$s) detect an effect size of %3$s%4$s, assuming a %5$s criterion for "
"detection that allows for a maximum Type I error rate of %6$s."
msgstr ""
"若要可靠地（機率大於或等於 %2$s）偵測到效果量 %3$s%4$s，並假設偵測的判斷準則"
"為 %5$s（其容許的最大型一誤差率為 %6$s），我們將需要 %1$s。"

msgid ""
"A design with %1$s will reliably (with probability greater than or equal to "
"%2$s) detect  effect sizes of %3$s%4$s, assuming a %5$s criterion for "
"detection that allows for a maximum Type I error rate of %6$s."
msgstr ""
"一個具有 %1$s 的設計，在假設偵測的判斷準則為 %5$s（其容許的最大型一誤差率為 "
"%6$s）之下，將能可靠地（機率大於或等於 %2$s）偵測到效果量 %3$s%4$s。"

msgid ""
"A design with %1$s can detect effect sizes of %2$s%3$s with a probability of "
"at least %4$s, assuming a %5$s criterion for detection that allows for a "
"maximum Type I error rate of %6$s."
msgstr ""
"一個具有 %1$s 的設計，在假設偵測的判斷準則為 %5$s（其容許的最大型一誤差率為 "
"%6$s）之下，能夠以至少 %4$s 的機率偵測到效果量 %2$s%3$s。"

msgid ""
"To evaluate the design specified in the table, we can consider how sensitive "
"it is to true effects of increasing sizes; that is, are we likely to "
"correctly conclude that %1$s when the effect size is large enough to care "
"about?"
msgstr ""
"若要評估表格中指定的設計，我們可以考量其對於逐漸增大之真實效果的敏感度；亦"
"即，當效果量大到值得關注時，我們是否有可能正確地推論出 %1$s？"

msgid ""
"The specified design leads to (an) unsolvable equation(s) while computing "
"the values for this power table. Try to enter less extreme values for the "
"parameters."
msgstr ""
"指定的設計在計算此檢定力表格的數值時導致方程式無解。請嘗試為參數設定較不極端"
"的數值。"

