msgid ""
"To evaluate the design specified in the table, we can consider how sensitive "
"it is to true effects of increasing sizes; that is, are we likely to "
"correctly conclude that %s when the effect size is large enough to care "
"about?"
msgstr ""
"若要評估表格中指定的設計，我們可以考量其對於逐漸增大之真實效果的敏感度；亦"
"即，當效果量大到值得關注時，我們是否有可能正確地推論出 %s？"

msgid "absolute difference in proportions"
msgstr "比例之絕對差異"

msgid ""
"Conversely, if one is satisfied to reliably detect only larger effect sizes, "
"smaller sample sizes are needed. The solid black curve on the contour plot "
"shows sample size/effect size combinations with a power of %1$s. The point "
"shows the specified design and %2$s."
msgstr ""
"反之，若僅滿足於可靠地偵測較大的效果量，則所需的樣本數較小。等值線圖上的黑色"
"實線曲線顯示出檢定力為 %1$s 時的樣本數與效果量組合。圖中的點則表示指定的設計"
"與 %2$s。"

msgid "sample sizes of %s"
msgstr "樣本數 %s"

msgid "effect sizes"
msgstr "效果量"

msgid "absolute differences in proportions"
msgstr "比例之絕對差異"

msgid "have power of at least %s"
msgstr "具有至少 %s 的檢定力"

msgid "only be sufficiently sensitive (power >%s)"
msgstr "僅在檢定力 >%s 時才具備足夠的敏感度"

msgid "sample sizes of at least %s"
msgstr "至少 %s 的樣本數"

msgid ""
"The figure above shows two sampling distributions: the sampling distribution "
"of the %1$s effect size when %2$s (left), and when %3$s (right)."
msgstr ""
"上圖顯示兩個抽樣分配：左側為當 %2$s 時 %1$s 效果量的抽樣分配，右側為當 %3$s "
"時的抽樣分配。"

msgid "Both assume %s."
msgstr "兩者皆假設 %s。"

msgid ""
"When the observed effect size is far enough away from 0 to be more extreme "
"than the %s we say we 'reject' the null hypothesis."
msgstr ""
"當觀察到的效果量與0的距離足夠遠，以致比 %s 更為極端時，我們稱之為「拒絕」虛無"
"假設。"

msgid ""
"On the other hand, if %1$s, the evidence would exceed the criterion  &mdash; "
"and hence we would correctly claim that %2$s &mdash; at least %3$s%% of the "
"time."
msgstr ""
"另一方面，若 %1$s，則證據會超過判斷準則 — 因此我們至少有 %3$s%% 的機率會正確"
"地宣稱 %2$s。"

msgid "Variance ratio (%s)"
msgstr "變異數比（%s）"

msgid "Power by variance ratio"
msgstr "以變異數比為變項的檢定力"

msgid "True variance ratio (%s)"
msgstr "真實變異數比（%s）"

msgid ""
"The power contour plot shows how the sensitivity of the test changes with "
"the hypothetical variance ratio and the sample sizes in the design. As we "
"increase the sample sizes, smaller variance ratios become reliably "
"detectable."
msgstr ""
"檢定力等值線圖顯示檢定的敏感度如何隨假設變異數比及設計中的樣本數而變化。當樣"
"本數增加時，較小的變異數比也能被可靠地偵測到。"

msgid ""
"Conversely, if one is satisfied to reliably detect only larger variance "
"ratios, smaller sample sizes are needed. The point shows the power of "
"specified  design and variance ratio."
msgstr ""
"反之，若僅滿足於可靠地偵測較大的變異數比，則所需的樣本數較小。圖中的點即表示"
"指定設計與變異數比下的檢定力。"

msgid "only be sufficiently sensitive (power > %1$s)"
msgstr "僅在檢定力 > %1$s 時才具備足夠的敏感度"

msgid ""
"The power curve above shows how the sensitivity of the test and design is "
"larger for larger variance ratios. If we obtained %1$s our test and design "
"would %2$s to variance ratios of %3$s%4$s."
msgstr ""
"上方的檢定力曲線顯示，對於較大的變異數比，檢定與設計的敏感度也較高。若我們獲"
"得 %1$s，則我們的檢定與設計對於 %3$s%4$s 的變異數比將 %2$s。"

msgid ""
"We would be more than likely to miss (power less than 50%%) variance ratios "
"of %s."
msgstr "對於變異數比 %s，我們將很有可能無法偵測到（檢定力低於 50%%）。"

msgid ""
"The power curve above shows how the sensitivity of the test and design is "
"larger for larger sample sizes. In order for our test and design to have "
"sufficient sensitivity (power > %1$s) to detect that %2$s when the variance "
"ratio is %3$s or more extreme, we would need %4$s."
msgstr ""
"上方的檢定力曲線顯示，對於較大的樣本數，檢定與設計的敏感度也較高。為了使我們"
"的檢定與設計在變異數比為 %3$s 或更極端時，具有足夠的敏感度（檢定力 > %1$s）以"
"偵測到該 %2$s，我們將需要 %4$s。"

msgid ""
"The figure above shows two sampling distributions: the sampling distribution "
"of the %1$s variance ratio when %2$s, and when %3$s%4$s."
msgstr ""
"上圖顯示兩個抽樣分配：當 %2$s 時的 %1$s 變異數比抽樣分配，以及當 %3$s%4$s 時"
"的抽樣分配。"

msgid ""
"When the observed variance ratio is far enough away from 1 to be more "
"extreme than the %1$s we say we 'reject' the null hypothesis."
msgstr ""
"當觀察到的變異數比與1的距離足夠遠，以致比 %1$s 更為極端時，我們稱之為「拒絕」"
"虛無假設。"

msgid ""
"We would need %1$s to reliably (with probability greater than %2$s) detect a "
"variance ratio of %3$s, assuming a %4$s criterion for detection that allows "
"for a maximum Type I error rate of %5$s."
msgstr ""
"若要可靠地（機率大於 %2$s）偵測到變異數比 %3$s，並假設偵測的判斷準則為 %4$s"
"（其容許的最大型一誤差率為 %5$s），我們將需要 %1$s。"

msgid ""
"A design with %1$s will reliably (with probability greater than %2$s) detect "
"variance ratios of %3$s, assuming a %4$s criterion for detection that allows "
"for a maximum Type I error rate of %5$s."
msgstr ""
"一個具有 %1$s 的設計，在假設偵測的判斷準則為 %4$s（其容許的最大型一誤差率為 "
"%5$s）之下，將能可靠地（機率大於 %2$s）偵測到變異數比 %3$s。"

msgid ""
"A design with %1$s can detect variance ratios of %2$s with a probability of "
"at least %3$s, assuming a %4$s criterion for detection that allows for a "
"maximum Type I error rate of %5$s."
msgstr ""
"一個具有 %1$s 的設計，在假設偵測的判斷準則為 %4$s（其容許的最大型一誤差率為 "
"%5$s）之下，能夠以至少 %3$s 的機率偵測到變異數比 %2$s。"

msgid ""
"To evaluate the design specified in the table, we can consider how sensitive "
"it is to true effects of increasing sizes; that is, are we likely to "
"correctly conclude that %1$s when the variance ratio is large enough to care "
"about?"
msgstr ""
"若要評估表格中指定的設計，我們可以考量其對於逐漸增大之真實效果的敏感度；亦"
"即，當變異數比大到值得關注時，我們是否有可能正確地推論出 %1$s？"

msgid ""
"To improve readability of this power table for a 'Two-sided' alternative "
"hypothesis, only the intervals in the direction of the specified variance "
"ratio are displayed under 'True variance ratio'"
msgstr ""
"為提升此檢定力表格在對立假設為「雙尾」時的可讀性，僅顯示指定變異數比方向下的"
"區間於「真實變異數比」欄位中"

msgid "Power Curve by variance ratio"
msgstr "以變異數比為變項的檢定力曲線"

msgid "Alternative hypothesis"
msgstr "對立假設"

msgid "Power by Effect Size"
msgstr "以效果量為變項的檢定力"

msgid "a sample size of %1$s in each group"
msgstr "各組樣本數皆為 %1$s"

msgid "group sample sizes of %1$s and %2$s respectively,"
msgstr "組別樣本數分別為 %1$s 與 %2$s，"

msgid ""
"A design with %1$s will reliably (with probability greater than or equal to "
